  <view class="content">
    <view class="title">以下是各时态的标志性时间词及用法说明，帮助更精准判断时态应用场景：</view>
    
    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">一、一般现在时（Present Simple）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：always, usually, often, sometimes, never, every day/week/month, on Sundays, in the morning/afternoon, etc.</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• She <text class="highlight">works</text> every day.（every day）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• They <text class="highlight">play</text> football on Sundays.（on Sundays）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">二、一般过去时（Past Simple）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：yesterday, last week/month/year, ago（如3 days ago）, in + 过去年份（in 2020）, the other day, just now, etc.</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• He <text class="highlight">did</text> his homework yesterday.（yesterday）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• They <text class="highlight">studied</text> in London last year.（last year）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">三、一般将来时（Future Simple）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：tomorrow, next week/month/year, in + 时间段（in 2 days/in the future）, soon, later, tonight, etc.</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• We <text class="highlight">will study</text> abroad next year.（next year）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• She <text class="highlight">will play</text> the piano tonight.（tonight）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">四、现在进行时（Present Continuous）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：now, at the moment, right now, listen, look, etc.（暗示正在进行的动作）。</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• They <text class="highlight">are playing</text> basketball now.（now）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• Look! She <text class="highlight">is working</text> on the project.（look）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">五、过去进行时（Past Continuous）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：at + 过去时间点（at 8:00 last night）, when/while引导的过去时间状语从句, this time yesterday, etc.</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• He <text class="highlight">was doing</text> homework at 9 pm yesterday.（at 9 pm yesterday）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• She <text class="highlight">was studying</text> when I called.（when引导的从句）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">六、现在完成时（Present Perfect）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：</view>
      <view class="sub-signal">• 表示"已完成"：already, yet, just, ever, never</view>
      <view class="sub-signal">• 表示"持续"：for + 时间段（for 3 years）, since + 时间点（since 2020）, so far, up to now, in the past/last + 时间段（in the past 5 years）</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• I <text class="highlight">have already done</text> the work.（already）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• They <text class="highlight">have studied</text> here for 2 years.（for 2 years）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">七、过去完成时（Past Perfect）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：by + 过去时间点（by yesterday/by the end of last year）, before + 过去时间, when/after引导的过去完成时从句（强调"过去的过去"）。</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• She <text class="highlight">had played</text> the piano before she went to bed.（before引导的过去时间）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• By last month, they <text class="highlight">had worked</text> here for 10 years.（by last month）</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">八、将来进行时（Future Continuous）</view>
      <view class="signal-words">标志词：at + 将来时间点（at 5 pm tomorrow）, this time tomorrow, by then, etc.（强调将来某刻正在进行的动作）。</view>
      <view class="example-title">示例：</view>
      <view class="example-item">• We <text class="highlight">will be studying</text> at 8 pm tomorrow.（at 8 pm tomorrow）</view>
      <view class="example-item">• She <text class="highlight">will be working</text> in the office this time next week.（this time next week）</view>
    </view>

